OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FBecoming dry
OL,6,Finto the evening, with extensive low
OL,7,Fcloud thinning and developing breaks
OL,8,Fovernight. Given the light winds, a
OL,9,Fwidespread frost is expected, with
OL,10,Fsome fog or freezing fog patches also
OL,11,Fpossible later in the night.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FA fine and frosty start in
OL,14,Fmany places, with areas of mist and
OL,15,Ffog clearing to a dry day, with light
OL,16,Fwinds and some sunshine. Becoming
OL,17,Fcloudier into the evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
