OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FMainly
OL,6,Fdry but with rather a lot of cloud
OL,7,Faround in this period, with some
OL,8,Fhaziness and morning fog. Becoming
OL,9,Fclearer but more unsettled Tuesday,
OL,10,Fwith wind and rain later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
